```
# Compiled Python files
*.pyc
__pycache__/

# Build and distribution directories
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Environment files
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# Logs
*.log

# Coverage reports
.coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/

# Translations - POT file (source) should be tracked, but compiled MO files should not
*.mo

# Virtual environments (if present)
.venv/
venv/
env/

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# Cache directories
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/
.cache/
```